  • public class Manifest
extends java.util.AbstractList<Truck>
    Author:
    Harrison Berryman - 09745092 Builds a manifest containing trucks.

    Builds a manifest that contains both refrigerated and ordinary trucks. The manifest states the truck's type and all item's it's carrying along with their quantities.
